  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><br><span></span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;padding: 1em;outline: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 4px;border-top-style: solid;border-right-style: solid;border-bottom-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(250, 81, 81);color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);font-size: 14px;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;border-radius: 6px;background: rgb(247, 247, 247);visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;\">作者：举个栗子（知乎）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1921218299133396032\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1921218299133396032</a></span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(10, 10, 10);letter-spacing: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;text-align: start;font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(10, 10, 10);letter-spacing: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;text-align: start;font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, system-ui, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\"><br></div><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\">\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px 8px 1.5em;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Qwen2.5的RL训练过程主要分为两阶段，第一阶段为离线阶段做DPO，第二阶段为在线阶段使用偏好RM做GRPO，两阶段RL主要是针对通用场景来做的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">不同于Qwen2.5，过去一段时间基于RL推理的大火为后训练带来了新的方向，Qwen3也着重在后训练阶段提升模型的推理能力，并且一个关键创新为</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">将思考模式和非思考模型集成到一个统一的框架中，这使得模型既拥有拥有复杂多步骤推理的能力（例如QwQ-32B），也能够基于上下文进行快速响应（例如GPT-4o）。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Qwen3是如何实现以上功能的呢？一图以蔽之</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-imgfileid=\"100017208\" data-ratio=\"0.4444444444444444\" title=\"null\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);display: block;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: inherit;font-size: 15px;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dbdf332a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1Apc68I5xm5diax7qs6fd74tzNGV0TFWF7H26Elhjod3lqWQzW4l0fSicI6MoHpicyl6z9487UUQQ6psrg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Qwen3-235B-A22B和Qwen3-32B使用四阶段的训练过程，前两个阶段侧重于提升模型的“思考”能力。接下来的两个阶段旨在将 “非思考” 功能集成到模型中。而Qwen3-30B及以下尺寸的模型采用蒸馏的方式，提升模型的Pass@1分数。接下来详细解读一下其四阶段的训练过程。</span></p>\n   <h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(250, 81, 81);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em auto 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">阶段一：冷启动训练</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">冷启动数据集主要覆盖数学、代码、逻辑推理、和STEM问题，这部分数据需要经过严格的筛选，否则冷启动训练后模型的通用能力可能会劣化，因此报告中说明他们对query和response分别都进行了筛选。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">1.Query筛选</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：目的是筛选出过于简单和难于验证的问题。前者使用Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct进行推理，如果不使用CoT即可回答正确，那么对这种query进行筛除；后者同样使用Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct，识别包含多个子问题和要求生成一般文本内容的问题，对这种query也进行筛除。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">2.Response筛选</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：使用QwQ-32B为每个query生成N个候选回复。对于QwQ-32B无法回答正确的问题，会人工再评估一遍回复的准确性；对于多个回答均正确的问题，会使用以下6个准则进一步筛选：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);list-style: circle;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （1）最终答案错误</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （2）包含大量重复</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （3）在没有充分推理的情况下明确猜测答案</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （4）think和summary内容不一致</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （5）包含多语种或风格跳变</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （6）和验证集过于相似，有以上问题的回答也会被筛除。</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Response筛除的目的是在模型中注入基础推理模式，但并不强调推理性能，这样保证模型的推理潜力不受限制且不过拟合，为第二阶段RL打下基础。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">报告中未提及冷启动阶段的数据量。</span></p>\n   <h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(250, 81, 81);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em auto 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">阶段二：RL推理能力训练</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">RL训练Query遵循以下4个原则进行筛选：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);list-style: circle;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （1）未在冷启动阶段使用</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （2）对于冷启动模型来说是可学习的</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （3）需要有一定的难度</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （4）包含多个领域。</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">满足以上四点后选择了</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">3995个query-verifier对（和冷启动的数据覆盖范围应该是一样的，但是这个数据量真的好少啊）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">，在GRPO训练过程中，通过控制模型的熵，对exploration和exploitation进行了平衡，从而实现平稳的训练。</span></p>\n   <h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(250, 81, 81);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em auto 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">阶段三：思考模式融合</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">这一阶段是通过SFT的方式对阶段二得到的模型进行微调，融合“思考”和“非思考”模式的推理。为了保证阶段二性能不受影响，这里“思考”训练数据采用阶段二模型在阶段一query数据上做拒绝采样得到；“非思考”数据涵盖各种任务，包括编码、数学、指令遵循、多语言任务、创意写作、问答和角色扮演。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">两种模式使用/think和/no_think标志进行区分</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">，注意“非思考模式”也有开始&lt;think&gt;和结束&lt;/think&gt;的标志符，只是其思考过程置为空。并且在训练过程中，会针对多轮对话进行“思考”和“非思考”模式的混合训练。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-imgfileid=\"100017209\" data-ratio=\"0.35185185185185186\" title=\"null\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);display: block;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: inherit;font-size: 15px;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f7b4a16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1Apc68I5xm5diax7qs6fd74tzNPx2m5nYMSdU86ibuFVBicNMGMZ8ic5y1O5Yrwd1hMMH37RQtXeeSicYnGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(250, 81, 81);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em auto 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">阶段四：通用RL</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">这一阶段旨在提升模型在不同场景下的通用能力和稳定性，涵盖了 20 多个不同的任务，针对不同任务有针对性的评分标准及奖励模型。目的在于提升以下多种任务下的能力：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);list-style: circle;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （1）指令跟随任务</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （2）融合思考模式的格式跟随任务</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （3）开放任务下与人类偏好对齐</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （4）多轮对话下的长期决策任务</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• （5）定制化任务如搜索等</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">具体地，他们采用三种不同的奖励：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);list-style: circle;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Rule-based reward</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：主要用在推理任务、指令跟随、格式跟随任务上</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Model-based Reward with Reference Answer</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：提供每个query的参考答案并提示 Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct 根据参考答案对response进行评分。这种方法无需严格的格式设置，进一步避免因为rule-based reward漏检造成的hacking问题</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Model-based Reward without Reference Answer</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：即基于人类偏好训练的BT model，用在通用任务上，提高模型的参与度和有用性</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(250, 81, 81);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em auto 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Strong-to-Weak Distillation</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">主要是针对小尺寸模型的蒸馏训练，也分成两阶段：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">1.Off-policy Distillation</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：使用 /think 和 /no_think 模式生成的教师模型(Qwen3-32B or Qwen3-235B-A22B)的输出结合起来进行蒸馏。这有助于提升小模型基本的推理能力和在不同思维模式之间切换的能力</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">2.On-policy Distillation</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：学生模型对query进行采样，在 /think 或 /no think 模式下生成回复。然后，通过将回复的logits 与教师模型的 logits对齐来微调学生模型，以最小化 KL 散度。</span></p>\n   <h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(250, 81, 81);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em auto 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">后训练效果评估</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">具体的测试分数就不一一展示了，参考原文，主要包括通用任务、对齐任务、数学、文本推理、Agent、代码、多语种测试任务。报告中展示了几个结论：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);list-style: circle;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• 旗舰MoE模型Qwen3-235B-A22B 在开源模型中，无论是思考模式还是非思考模式，都展示了最先进的整体性能，超越了 DeepSeek-R1 和 DeepSeek-V3 等开源模型。Qwen3-235B-A22B 还与 OpenAI-o1、Gemini2.5-Pro 和 GPT-4o 等闭源模型展示出了很强的竞争力。</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• 旗舰Dense模型 Qwen3-32B 在大多数基准测试中都优于之前的最强推理模型 QwQ-32B，并且与闭源 OpenAI-o3mini 的性能相当，。Qwen3-32B 在非思考模式下的性能也非常出色，超越了Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct。</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">• 轻量级模型，包括 Qwen3-30B-A3B、Qwen3-14B 和其他较小的Dense模型，始终优于参数数量接近或较大的开源模型，证明了 Strong-to-Weak Distillation 方法的成功。</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">报告里还讨论了几个有趣的发现，首先是之前在推理长度上的scaling law，从下图中可以看到，Qwen3-235B-A22B 随着输出长度的增加（1K-&gt;32K）在AIME、LiveCodeBench、GPQA Diamond测试集上性能都有所提升。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-imgfileid=\"100017212\" data-ratio=\"0.6851851851851852\" title=\"null\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);display: block;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: inherit;font-size: 15px;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0f73ef26&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1Apc68I5xm5diax7qs6fd74tzNNpOJYS4EHLmadh75HJoHSCRXqRRiaxJHFTZGBBMT04BCdtgdqAMfUUw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">其次，小模型直接从教师模型进行蒸馏比直接做强化学习的性能要好，同时所需的时间也更少。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100017210\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.22777777777777777\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);display: block;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: inherit;font-size: 15px;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bfdd0c44&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1Apc68I5xm5diax7qs6fd74tzNqwHJ15Sb7B3mbKr3Tls5Uq8umtUIvkGCicW55iciajLPuWBo71loRRC3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">另外，他们还做了阶段三和阶段四的消融实验，这里还引入了一些验证幻觉的任务、控制长度的写作任务、混合思考模式下的多轮对话任务、工具调用任务，结果如下图。可以看出，阶段三提升了模型在“思考”模式下的指令跟随、格式跟随能力；第四阶段则进一步提升了这种能力；然而对于知识、STEM、数学和编码任务，阶段三、四的训练并没有带来显着的改进。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">相比之下，对于像 AIME'24 和 LiveCodeBench 这样难度较高的任务，“思考”模式下的性能实际上会下降。推测这种退化是由于模型在更广泛的通用任务上进行了训练，这可能会损害模型处理复杂问题的专业能力，他们认为这种退化在性能的权衡下是可接受的范围。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-imgfileid=\"100017211\" data-ratio=\"0.49907407407407406\" title=\"null\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);display: block;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: inherit;font-size: 15px;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=593c8a7e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1Apc68I5xm5diax7qs6fd74tzNzLgic3ghukHJVOdKiaj0NtiadQGF78ibOkYd1R1KHzwrrVzNASMXb7eopA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></figure></div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "详细解读了 Qwen3 大模型独特的四阶段 RL 训练过程，该过程创新性地融合了模型的思考与非思考能力，并展示了其在推理能力上的显著提升。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "详细解读了 Qwen3 大模型独特的四阶段 RL 训练过程，该过程创新性地融合了模型的思考与非思考能力，并展示了其在推理能力上的显著提升。",
  "summary": "文章深入剖析了 Qwen3 大语言模型独特的四阶段强化学习（RL）后训练过程，旨在提升模型的推理能力。与 Qwen2.5 的两阶段 RL 不同，Qwen3 的核心创新在于将“思考”模式和“非思考”模式集成到统一框架中，使其既能进行复杂的多步骤推理，也能基于上下文快速响应。该训练过程包括：第一阶段“冷启动训练”通过严格筛选数据注入基础推理模式；第二阶段“RL 推理能力训练”利用精选数据进行 GRPO 训练以提升推理深度；第三阶段“思考模式融合”通过 SFT 将两种模式融合，并引入`/think`和`/no_think`标志；第四阶段“通用 RL”则通过多种奖励机制提升模型在 20 多个任务上的通用能力和稳定性。此外，文章还介绍了针对小尺寸模型的“强弱蒸馏”方法，通过教师模型高效传递推理和模式切换能力。评估结果显示，Qwen3 系列模型在各项基准测试中均表现卓越，与顶尖闭源模型具备竞争力，并揭示了推理长度扩展、蒸馏优于直接 RL 以及通用性与专业性权衡等有趣发现。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Qwen3 采用四阶段 RL 训练，创新性融合了模型的“思考”与“非思考”模式。",
      "explanation": "这种统一框架使模型既具备复杂多步骤推理能力，又能基于上下文快速响应，显著提升了模型在通用和特定任务上的表现。"
    },
    {
      "point": "冷启动与 RL 推理阶段通过严格数据筛选，为模型注入基础推理模式并提升潜力。",
      "explanation": "精心筛选高质量的数学、代码、逻辑推理数据，并结合 RL 训练，确保模型在不牺牲通用能力的前提下，增强推理深度和稳定性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "强弱蒸馏方法高效提升小模型推理能力，且优于直接强化学习。",
      "explanation": "通过教师模型（大模型）的输出对小模型进行蒸馏训练，显著提升了轻量级模型的 Pass@1 分数和综合性能，同时降低了训练成本和时间。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "将思考模式和非思考模型集成到一个统一的框架中，这使得模型既拥有拥有复杂多步骤推理的能力（例如 QwQ-32B），也能够基于上下文进行快速响应（例如 GPT-4o）。",
    "Response 筛除的目的是在模型中注入基础推理模式，但并不强调推理性能，这样保证模型的推理潜力不受限制且不过拟合，为第二阶段 RL 打下基础。",
    "小模型直接从教师模型进行蒸馏比直接做强化学习的性能要好，同时所需的时间也更少。",
    "旗舰 MoE 模型 Qwen3-235B-A22B 在开源模型中，无论是思考模式还是非思考模式，都展示了最先进的整体性能，超越了 DeepSeek-R1 和 DeepSeek-V3 等开源模型。",
    "推测这种退化是由于模型在更广泛的通用任务上进行了训练，这可能会损害模型处理复杂问题的专业能力，他们认为这种退化在性能的权衡下是可接受的范围。"
